    Scope and Contents
These papers document the effort to establish interdisciplinary degree programs at SSU.  The material in these drafts has its final form in  "Guide to Sangamon State University,"  SSU's first catalogue in the escriptions of four programs- Work, Leisure, Poverty &amp; Power, Justice and the Social Order; Communication and Modern Technology; Man and his Environment.  
  
